    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――月のテンペストのライブ数日前",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……もうすぐ月ストのライブ当日か\nまさか、麻奈の誕生日にライブとはなぁ",
      "startTime": 6.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "しかも、あの時のバースデーライブと同じ会場だなんて\nあいつが知ったら、なんて言うかな……",
      "startTime": 14.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "もっちろん、私もゲストで出るからね！",
      "startTime": 18.0029246409,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01_short/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_mean-09.m4a",
      "text": "全世界がずっと待ってた姉妹共演だもん",
      "startTime": 21.7562601169,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……なんて言いそうだよなぁ\nまぁ、今回はゲストとして、遙子さんが出るんだが",
      "startTime": 28.9333344778,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈の誕生日に――\n琴乃のライブに、遙子さんが出るのか……",
      "startTime": 35.9000011445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――2017年",
      "startTime": 40.759594218,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-00-000-noon",
      "startTime": 41.9262593587
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01_short/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_hey-03.m4a",
      "text": "会場、押さえられたって本当！？",
      "startTime": 42.7929260969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、本当だ\n今年は出来るぞ、長瀬麻奈バースデーライブ",
      "startTime": 47.6666678112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01_short/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_laughter-08.m4a",
      "text": "やったー！　ありがとう{user}くん！",
      "startTime": 51.5338566382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01_short/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_thank-01.m4a",
      "text": "もう、去年からずーっとずーーっと……",
      "startTime": 55.2338578302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01_short/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-04.m4a",
      "text": "ずーーーーっと、やりたかったから、嬉しい！",
      "startTime": 59.9338594356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "本当に出来るんだぁ、バースデーライブ……",
      "startTime": 64.3405267378,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}